        "id": "frequently-asked-questions",
        "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "content": "<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>How do I verify my email address?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">When you sign up, a verification email is sent automatically. Click the link in that email to verify your account. If you didn't receive it, check your spam folder.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>Can I enroll in multiple services?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">Yes! You can enroll in multiple services. Some services may have enrollment limits, which will be shown as \"Limit Reached\" if applicable.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>What happens when I pause a service?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">When you pause a service, your broker account is temporarily deactivated, but all your data is preserved. You can reactivate at any time to resume the service.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>Is removing a service permanent?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">Yes. When you remove a service, your service agreement and broker account connection are permanently deleted and cannot be recovered.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>How do I know if I have unpaid invoices?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">A warning badge will appear on the \"Payments & Billing\" link in the navigation if you have unpaid invoices.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>Why can't I save my phone number?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">Phone numbers must be exactly 10 digits (numbers only). The system will automatically format it for you.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-4\"><strong>How do I change my email address?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-4\">For security reasons, email addresses cannot be changed through the portal. Please contact support for assistance.</p>"
